# Tests

- Use Vitest with `@testing-library/react` and `@testing-library/user-event`.
- Prefer `getByRole` and `getByLabelText` over `getByTestId` unless necessary.
- Mock modules with `vi.mock()`; use `vi.importActual` when extending real modules.
- Run `afterEach(cleanup)` from setup for isolation.
